title: Outfit Idea | Off The Shoulder + Gladiator Sandals
content: Dressing for Spring can be so fun... the cute headpieces, interesting sandals and a fresh new makeup look. I have been loving dark lips so much lately, and I am always into the whole white top / blue jeans combo. My sister is making me a floral headpiece this week so I can't wait to get my hands on it. x Vanessa
source: FLIP AND STYLE | Sydney Fashion and Beauty Blog + Youtuber
